'''''Written Communication''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] that publishes papers in the field of [[writing|written communication]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Chad Wickman ([[Auburn University]]). It was established in 1984 and is currently published by [[SAGE Publications]].
== Abstracting and indexing == ''Written Communication'' is abstracted and indexed in [[Scopus]], and the [[Social Sciences Citation Index]]. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', its 2017 [[impact factor]] is 1.267, ranking it 44 out of 84 journals in the category "Communication".<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2011 |chapter=Journals Ranked by Impact: Communication |title=2017 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Social Sciences |accessdate=2017-07-05 |series=Web of Science |postscript=.}}</ref>
